quran[78]{c,v,t}:
  55,1,The Mercy-giving
  55,2,has taught the Reading
  55,3,created man
  55,4,taught him self-expression
  55,5,"The sun and moon [move along] like clockwork"
  55,6,shrubs and trees both bend in worship
  55,7,"while He has raised the sky up and placed scales [there]"
  55,8,so you may not skimp in weighing
  55,9,"Always measure accurately with [all]fairness and do not give short weight"
  55,10,The earth has He laid out for humanity
  55,11,"offering fruit, datepalms bearing blossoms"
  55,12,"grain wrapped up in husks, and fragrant herbs"
  55,13,So which of your Lord´s benefits will both of you deny
  55,14,He created man from ringing clay just as a potter does
  55,15,while He created sprites from the glow in fire
  55,16,So which of your Lord´s benefits will you both deny
  55,17,Lord of both Easts and Lord of both Wests
  55,18,So which of our Lord´s benefits will both of you deny
  55,19,He has loosed both seas which still come together
  55,20,between them lies an isthmus which neither tries to cross
  55,21,So which of your Lord´s benefits will both of you deny
  55,22,He produces pearls and coral from them both
  55,23,so which of our Lord´s benefits will both of you deny
  55,24,His are the vessels looming up like landmarks on the sea
  55,25,so which of our Lord´s benefits will both of you deny
  55,26,Everyone upon it will disappear
  55,27,while your Lord´s face will remain full of majesty and splendor
  55,28,So which of our Lord´s benefits will both of you deny
  55,29,"Everyone in Heaven and Earth asks for something from Him; each day He is [Busy] at some task"
  55,30,So which of our Lord´s benefits will both of you deny
  55,31,We shall finish off both loads for you
  55,32,so which of our Lord´s benefits will both of you deny
  55,33,"company of sprites and humankind, if you can manage to penetrate beyond the realms of Heaven and Earth and then pass beyond them! Yet you will only penetrate them through some authority"
  55,34,So which of our Lord´s benefits will both of you deny
  55,35,"A flare of fire and sparks will be loosed against you, from which neither of you will be protected"
  55,36,so which of our Lord´s benefits will both of you deny
  55,37,"When the sky splits open and becomes like a rose [painted] by some artist"
  55,38,so which of your Lord´s benefits will both of you deny
  55,39,"On that day, no man nor any sprite will be questioned about any offence of his"
  55,40,so which of your Lord´s benefits will both of you deny
  55,41,"Criminals will be recognized by their features, and seized by their forelocks and feet"
  55,42,so which of your Lord´s benefits will both of you deny
  55,43,"Such is Hell, which criminals deny exists"
  55,44,They will circle around between it and a seething bath
  55,45,So which of your Lord´s benefits will both of you deny
  55,46,Yet anyone who fears to stand before his Lord will have two gardens
  55,47,so which of your Lord´s benefits will both of you deny
  55,48,Both containing many sorts of things
  55,49,so which of your Lord´s will both of you deny
  55,50,Each will have two flowing springs
  55,51,so which of your Lord´s benefits will both of you deny
  55,52,Each will have a pair forever kind of fruit
  55,53,so which of your Lord´s benefits will both of you deny
  55,54,They will recline on couches upholstered in brocade while the harvest from both orchards droops nearby
  55,55,so which of your Lord´s benefits will both of you deny
  55,56,"Bashful maidens will be there whom no human being has tampered with previously, nor an sprite"
  55,57,So which of your Lord´s benefits will both of you deny
  55,58,They will be like rubies and coral
  55,59,so which of your Lord´s benefits will both of you deny
  55,60,Is there any reward for kindness except kindness itself
  55,61,So which of your Lord´s benefits will both of you deny? Two Extra Gardens
  55,62,"Besides both of these, there will be two extra gardens"
  55,63,so which of your Lord´s benefits will both of you deny
  55,64,Both densely shaded
  55,65,so which of your Lord´s benefits will both of you deny
  55,66,Each will have two splashing fountains
  55,67,so which of your Lord´s benefits will both of you deny´
  55,68,"Both will have fruit, datepalms and pomegranates"
  55,69,so which of your Lord´s benefits will both of you deny
  55,70,"In them there will be the best, the fairest women"
  55,71,So which of your Lord´s benefits will both of you deny
  55,72,Bright-eyed damsels sheltered in pavilions
  55,73,so which of your Lord´s benefits will both of you deny
  55,74,"Whom no human being has tainted previously, nor any sprites"
  55,75,So which of your Lord´s benefits will both of you deny
  55,76,They will lean back on green cushions and handsome carpets
  55,77,so which of your Lord´s benefits will both of you deny
  55,78,"Blessed be your Lord´s name, Possessor of Majesty and Splendor"